OL,6,FHealth bosses in have committed to
OL,7,Fproviding patients with clear and
OL,8,Feasily accessible details of hospital
OL,9,Fwaiting lists.
OL,11,FIt comes after changes to Jersey's
OL,12,Fwebsite last year saw figures removed
OL,13,Fand then replaced by lengthy health
OL,14,Fboard papers.
OL,16,FJersey's monthly health board papers
OL,17,Fare created for staff meetings, rather
OL,18,Fthan patients, and do not specify
OL,19,Fwhere someone is in the queue.
