OL,3,CPatients call for hospital waiting
OL,4,Clist clarity
OL,6,FFormer patient Annette Brown, who
OL,7,Fwaited 14 months for her operation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "You need to know - you
OL,9,Fabsolutely need to know.
OL,11,F"I can't begin to tell you how
OL,12,Fdepressed I felt - I couldn't do
OL,13,Fanything and it's the waiting it's
OL,14,Fjust really hard to wait so long you
OL,15,Fknow".
OL,17,FJersey's health bosses have now
OL,18,Fcommitted to reinstating the monthly
OL,19,Fwaiting list data online for patients
OL,20,Fby the end of March 2024.
