OL,3,CPatients call for hospital waiting
OL,4,Clist clarity
OL,6,FSaying: "Information about waiting
OL,7,Flists is currently available every
OL,8,Fmonth and presented to the Health and
OL,9,FCommunity Advisory Board.
OL,11,F"In addition to this, we will be
OL,12,Fpublishing the average waiting times
OL,13,Ffor procedures on our website by the
OL,14,Fend of this month.
OL,16,F"However, our ultimate aim is to give
OL,17,Fpatients an indication of when they
OL,18,Fwill next be seen, during their face
OL,19,Fto face consultation with a clinician."
